name: CakeWSwap
description: CakeWSwap is a decentralized swap on ETHW chain and BSC chain with high APR on farming and lowest fees. CakeWSwap helps you make the most out of your crypto in three ways: Trade, Earn and Win. CAKEW is the delicious token that powers the CakeWSwap ecosystem. Earn CAKEW from Farms and Syrup Pools, win it in the lottery, or buy it on the exchange, then explore its use cases: * Stake it in Syrup Pools to earn free tokens * Use it in Yield Farms to earn more CAKEW * Buy Lottery tickets in the CakeWSwap Lottery * Participate in IFO Token Sales * Create your CakeWSwap Profile and mint NFTs * Vote on proposals relating to the CakeWSwap ecosystem
